                    "body": "The concept of scalars would still exist (e.g. in expressions, options) so there's still potential for confusion though this would reduce it. Aggregations would presumably still return scalars, too.\r\n\r\nIt does seem being able to accept scalars is more confusing than it's worth, though.",
